data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home. This property boasts a classic brick exterior, not only adding to its timeless appeal but also ensuring durability and low maintenance for years to come. Step inside to discover a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout the well-appointed living spaces. The home features three cozy bedrooms, offering versatility for a growing family or the perfect setup for a home office or guest room. Once of the standout features of this residence is its FIVE-YEAR-OLD HVAC system, providing comfort and energy efficiency. This recent upgrade adds value and peace of mind, ensuring you can enjoy a climate-controlled environment in every season. The covered patio in the backyard provides excellent space for outdoor entertaining, family gatherings, or just relaxing in the fresh air. The property sits on a generous half-acre lot, providing ample space for a variety of outdoor activities. Whether you have a green thumb and dream of creating your own garden oasis or envision a play area for children the possibilities are endless on this expansive lot. Additional features include a convenient storage shed in the backyard, offering extra space for tools, equipment or storage needs. For investors, the property presents an excellent opportunity with its attractive features and location. Whether you're looking for an investment property with great rental potential or a family home with room to grow, this residence is a MUST SEE. Don't miss out on the chance to make this house your home or a lucrative addition to your investment portfolio.
